{
  "stem": "17426.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 78.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we continue on our [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very, very loving relationship.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And she offered to hide me when she heard that they are going to close all the labor camps and deport the inmates to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She begged me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her father came with her once and begged me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I just could not see myself cooped up in a basement, fear-- with fear of every moment when I hear soldiers go by, or army people go by, or people talk-- that I will be discovered, in which case they, too, would be punished.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was a supreme sacrifice that they offered me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it-- I was very grateful for it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I just could not see my father and myself survive under these conditions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was still-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it's worth remembering that I was still not so bad off as most of the inmates were.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I still had some extra bread, and I still had some extra food that she brought me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was still getting an extra soup, because I was the dentist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I still had an extra privilege to go out of camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you know, altogether it wasn't something that was so pressing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was so final for me, going to another camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But little did I know that we were to be transported to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When was the last time you saw Zosia?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw Zosia at about the beginning of August, perhaps as late as the 10th of August.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] In our last meeting, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] she offered to [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] never give up her love for me.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
